Go to slack.comClick “Get Started” and then “My team isn’t using Slack yet.”Enter your email.
Go to the email Slack just sent you to retrieve the code and enter it.
On the next screen, you can enter the names and email addresses of people you’d like to add to your Slack workspace, and Slack will send them invitations.
Click “Finish” to complete your setup and click “Explore Slack” to start using Slack.
Join an existing workspaceTo join an existing Slack workspace, you’ll need to get permission from whoever owns that workspace.